            {
              "url": "/uploads/1779430661344-kdym-pt_en_01-835x420.JPEG",
              "name": "pt_en_01-835x420.JPEG",
              "type": "image",
              "size": 93110,
              "width": null,
              "height": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "- Click the 'Assign Partner' option on the selected fan page.",
          "media": [
            {
              "url": "/uploads/1779430665890-ae1c-pt_en_02-835x420.JPEG",
              "name": "pt_en_02-835x420.JPEG",
              "type": "image",
              "size": 91619,
              "width": null,
              "height": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "- Click 'Business ID' in the partner assignment popup.",
          "media": [
            {
              "url": "/uploads/1779430673291-4fg7-pt_en_03-835x420.JPEG",
              "name": "pt_en_03-835x420.JPEG",
              "type": "image",
              "size": 67968,
              "width": null,
              "height": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "- Enter the Nasmedia Business ID (793587697339145) in the 'Enter partner business ID' field.\n- After entering the Business ID, grant the minimum permissions required for ad operations.\n(Required options: Content, Ads, Insights)\n- After selecting the permissions, click the 'Assign' button.",
          "media": [
